# Task mapping:
#   1-3  →  gaussian  (seeds 42, 43, 44)
#   4-6  →  mog       (seeds 42, 43, 44)
#   7-9  →  flow      (seeds 42, 43, 44)
#
# Prerequisites:  bash batch/setup_gpu.sh   (one-time, on login node)
